{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Lift Sanctions on Iran and Restore Trade Relations",
        "additional_details": "Iran has suffered severe damage to its civilian infrastructure following the bombing by the United States and Israel. The country now needs urgent support to rebuild and help ordinary civilians recover.",
        "background": "We call on the UK Government to lift sanctions on Iran, work with international partners, including the European Union, to reverse the snapback of JCPOA-related measures, return to the nuclear deal, and restore lawful trade and economic relations with Iran.",
